<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><a href="/scp-4352">SCP-4352</a></strong></span> &#8212; <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>故事时间</strong></span></p>
<p>&quot;<em>我们不是第一个来管这东西的。有前人在我们之前做了点事，他们打得一手好牌。</em>&quot;</p>
<p>作者：<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5190300); return false;">Henzoid</a></span>和<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;">Tanhony</a></span>.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><a href="/scp-4428">Dr. Michaels</a></strong></span> &#8212; <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Michaels博士沒有處於危險之中</strong></span></p>
<p>&quot;<em>我们尽力了， 但是&#8230;我觉得这还没完。Jeremy，撑住。</em>&quot;</p>
<p>作者：<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span>和<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5190300); return false;">Henzoid</a></span>.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><a href="/scp-4467">SCP-4467</a></strong></span> &#8212; <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>哦，我明白了</strong></span></p>
<p>&quot;<em>本部的高光时刻。这是对语言工程的颠覆和挑战棘手异常的胜利。</em>&quot;</p>
<p>作者：<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;">DarkStuff</a></span>.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
